      143.53,
      523.0,
      176.5
    ],
    "text": "The accused appellant (hereinafter sometimes referred to as the appellant) was indicted by the Hon. Attorney General for possessing 3 grams of Diacetyl Morphine.",
    "fonts": [
      "Helvetica"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      10.954754829406738,
