  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      69.43,
      315.12,
      522.8,
      382.66
    ],
    "text": "3. Dock statement and the defence witness of the appellant was not considered. It is noted that the counsel for the appellant moves court to send this case to the High Court for re-trial. Primarily I wish to consider the second ground of appeal.",
    "fonts": [
      "Helvetica"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      10.743424415588379,
      10.780771255493164,
      11.151999473571777,
