      12.189091682434082
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      69.05,
      391.93,
      522.65,
      425.14
    ],
    "text": "The learned trial judge has perused the police notes while writing the judgment to vitiate the contradictions which amount to a misdirection of law.",
