    "bbox": [
      65.22,
      116.71,
      518.95,
      184.42
    ],
    "text": "On the 30th of November 1998 Police Sargent 2269 Weerasinghe who was attached to the Police Narcotics Bureau (PNB) received an information through his private informant that a person taking heroine for packing. Being satisfied with the information he reported to his superior Inspector of Police (I.P) Sunil Padmasiri Perera",
    "fonts": [
      "Helvetica",
      "Times-Roman"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      7.900100231170654,
      11.17397689819336,
      11.21309757232666,
      11.354860305786133,
      11.371907234191895,
      11.379045486450195,
      11.393664360046387,
